    "shortHook": "A one-year macro momentum map.",
    "patternNote": "The darkest countries include Guyana, Libya, Ireland, while the lightest include Equatorial Guinea, Iran, Islamic Rep., Haiti; that contrast is the fastest way to read the gdp growth pattern.",
